title: Uplink; The Original Game Soundtrack
description:
This is the soundtrack from PC Game "Uplink," by Introversion Software. The Soundtrack itself was never published in a mainstream format nor released for sale, however it was released, in its entirety, on the Uplink Developers CD in .s3m format... Not everyone uses .s3m, so I decided to convert them into the more user-friendly mp3 format so all can enjoy the music from the game, without having to actually play said game... Enjoy!
